general employees stock purchase plan (gespp):
in may2012, shareholders approved an additional 30 million shares for issuance under the companys gespp, increasing the number of approved shares to 60 million shares. substantially all employees are eligible to participate in the plan. participants are granted options at 85% of market value at the date of grant. there are no gespp shares under option at the beginning or end of each year because options are granted on the first business day and exercised on the last business day of the same month.
